snippet.textDisplay:
The sweetest little baby 😍
We're spoiled to get this cute video for her birthday, and it's just so nice to see a clip of her working but laughing and having fun too. People forget that this is the sort of thing that goes on behind the scenes for kpop artists constantly, so saying they have nothing to do except produce a comeback is way off.
Everyone needs to be patient, trust the girls when they say their music is coming, and realise that they work hard enough without being pressured to do even more by selfish fans.
